thread.title: Vincent

author: Vincent
title: Vincent
text: I have used inkfarm.com twice now. I purchase the double pack of XL cartridges for my Cannon printer. The service is easy to use and delivery is fast. The quality of the ink/cartridges are as good as factory. I can't tell the difference between factory Cannon ink and ink farm.com ink. With three college students in my house, we go thru ink fast. This dad is so glad I came across this web site.
